	dprr:hasNoteText "Tr. Mil., XXVIvir, q. pro pr. in the early Augustan period (CIL 6.1317-ILS 909). Possibly a son of the praetor of 62 (35; MRR 2.173) and a senator by 31. (TJC) See Suolahti, Junior Officers 316, 406; De Laet, no. 277.\n" .
